plot: Cutter grapples with Claudia's disappearance after he returns to a very different present than the one he left. Soon after, the team are called in to capture a pack of raptors on the loose at a local shopping center.

While Cutter grapples with Claudia Brown's disappearance, and tries to make sense of his confused mind, the anomalies make another appearance. This time a shopping mall has been targeted by ferocious Raptors and the team is called in to deal with the situation. Faced with an unknown terror, Cutter and the team rely on their wits to get the monsters back through the anomaly.—ITV's website
